#625  Abattoir escapes from Arkham Asylum and wreaks havoc at a political rally attended by Bruce Wayne and Vicki Vale. 

#626  The deadly vigilante known as the Electrocutioner has seemingly returned from the grave. Can the Batman find a way to stop this electrifying menace before it's too late? 

#627  Special 80-page anniversary issue! Celebrating the Dark Knight's 600th appearance in the pages of Detective Comics, relive Batman's origin from Detective Comics #27 with the original tale and updated versions exploring the Caped Crusader throughout the ages. 

#628  Someone is stealing hearts in Gotham City...the hearts of birds from the Penguin's Aerie. 

#629  A new drug has hit the streets of Gotham City, one that causes a person to relive the past evils of others. 

#630  The Dark Knight investigates a case connecting a contract killer, Siamese twin hitmen, and a book about the history of the stiletto heel.
